<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><author>Sobir Umurov</author>
<title>Xudovand umidim</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Kiyinchiliklar kupdir, vasvasalar kup
 Tanamizda mador yok, jonimizda orom
 Neki bulmasin Iso xolis bir orzuyim bor
 Senga xizmat kilaman, Nomingni Seni uluglab

[C1]
   Yurag ezilsa xam kaygurmayman
   Ulim vodiysida yursam xam kurkmayman
   Umidim bor, U xayotdir, Unga aytar suzim bor
   Senga xizmat kilaman, Nomingni Seni uluglab

[V2]
 Baʼzan imon susayar, kolmas suzlar duoda
 Taslim bulgim keladi vasvasayu sinovda
 Lekin Sen meni eltasan kutarib kullaringda
 Senga xizmat kilaman Nomingni Seni uluglab
 Omin!</lyrics>
</song>